roles-antag-clockwork-master-name = Prophet of Ratvar
roles-antag-clockwork-master-objective = Lead your team, assign roles, send some to recruit new cultists, others to gather resources, set up defenses. Open portals and bring the fallen back into action.
roles-antag-clockwork-master-rules = You are a [color=red][bold]Team Antagonist[/bold][/color], the living voice of Ratvar. Command and distribute the followers. Teleport the fallen back and heal them, and open the portal. Do not harm the station or its crew excessively—they are Ratvar’s property, and unnecessary violence may incur his wrath.

roles-antag-clockwork-cultist-name = Servant of Ratvar
roles-antag-clockwork-cultist-objective = Follow the will of the Prophet, assist the cult in achieving its objectives. Cooperate with other followers by gathering resources, recruiting new servants, and maintaining defenses.
roles-antag-clockwork-cultist-rules = You are a [color=red][bold]Team Antagonist[/bold][/color] alongside the rest of the Clockwork Cult. You answer to the Prophet. Carry out his orders, guard Ratvar’s tomb, and bring those capable of understanding Ratvar’s power to the altar for conversion. Do not harm the ordinary station crew—Ratvar needs his flock.
